vennela &lt;unk&gt; ( english : one and half ) is a 2013 telugu romantic comedy film directed by vennela kishore and produced by vasu kishore on vyjayanthi movies banner and directed by vennela kishore . starring vennela kishore , monal gajjar , kota srinivasa rao and brahmanandam in the lead roles and music composed by sunil kashyap . the film is a remake of telugu film vennela kishore . vennela kishore , monal gajjar , kota srinivasa rao and brahmanandam in the lead roles and music composed by sunil kashyap . the film recorded as super hit at the box office .